it.emarolab.amor.owlDebugger

Class Logger.LoggerFlag

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.emarolab.amor.owlDebugger.Logger.LoggerFlag
  • Enclosing class:
    Logger

    public static class Logger.LoggerFlag
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains defualts methods for enabling and disabling logging. Generically, each class of this architecture has a Logger attached to it. Use this static implementation to manipulate their flags.
